        <briefdescription>
<para>Computes the linear interpolation weight for a given frequency. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Calculates the interpolated superphoton weight between precomputed values in the weight table based on the input frequency <computeroutput>nu</computeroutput>.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>nu</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The frequency at which to compute the interpolated weight (\omega). </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>The computed linearly interpolated superphoton weight. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
